quran[44]{c,v,t}:
  37,139,Futhi ngempela uYunus (uJona) wayengomunye wezithunywa
  37,140,Khumbula ngenkathi egijima eya emkhunjini ogcwele
  37,141,"Manjalo\twaphonsa\tinkatho\twayeseba\tngomunye wabalahlekelweyo"
  37,142,Ngakho-ke inhlanzi yamgwinya kulapho yena efanelwe ukusolwa
  37,143,Kepha ukuba wayengesiyena omunye wabadumisayo
  37,144,Ngempela wayezohlala esiswini sayo (inhlanzi) kuze kube wusuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo
  37,145,Ngakho-ke samphonsa ogwini olomile kulapho yena egula
  37,146,Futhi samilisa isihlahla soselwa phezulu kwakhe
  37,147,Futhi samthumela kwabayinkulungwane noma ngaphezulu
  37,148,"Ngakho-ke\tbakholwa,\tsabe\tsesibanika\tinjabulo okwesikhashana"
  37,149,Ngakho-ke babuze ngakube okweNkosi yakho ngamadodakazi okwabo ngamadodana na
  37,150,Noma sadala izingelosi zabangabesifazane kulapho bona bebhekile
  37,151,Ngempela kungamanga abo abakushoyo
  37,152,"(Ukuthi)\tUmvelinqangi\twazala\tfuthi\tngempela\tbona banamanga"
  37,153,Wakhetha amadodakazi ngaphezulu kwamadodana na
  37,154,Kwenzekani ngani nehlulela kanjani
  37,155,Lapho-ke ngeke ukhunjuzwe
  37,156,Noma ninegunya elicacile na
  37,157,Ngakho-ke lethani incwadi yenu uma kungukuthi nineqiniso
  37,158,"Futhi benza ubudlelwane phakathi kwakhe namaJinn, futhi ngempela amaJinn azi kahle ukuthi ngempela wona ayolethwa ngaphambili"
  37,159,"Makadunyiswe\tuMvelinqangi\tngaphezulu\tkwalokho abakuchazayo"
  37,160,Ngaphandle kwezinceku zikaMvelinqangi ezimsulwa
  37,161,Ngakho-ke nina kanye nalokho enikukhonzayo
  37,162,Angeke nibalinge ngaye
  37,163,Ngaphandle kwalowo onqunyelwe ukusha esihogweni
  37,164,Futhi akekho namunye wethu ngaphandle kwalowo onendawo eyaziwayo
  37,165,Futhi ngempela thina sime ngolayini
  37,166,Futhi ngempela thina singabadumisayo
  37,167,Futhi babejwayele ukuthi
  37,168,Ukube sasinaso isikhumbuzo esinjengesabantu basendulo
  37,169,Sasizoba yizinceku zikaMvelinqangi eziqotho
  37,170,"Kepha abakholelwanga kusona, ngakho-ke bayokwazi"
  37,171,"Futhi ngempela izwi lethu selahamba ngaphambili laya ezincekwini zethu, izithunywa"
  37,172,Ngempela zona okwazo ukwelekelelwa
  37,173,Futhi ngempela amabutho ethu okwawo ukunqoba
  37,174,Ngakho-ke suka kubona kuze kube yisikhashana
  37,175,Futhi babone ngakho-ke nabo bazobona
  37,176,Ngakube yisijeziso sethu abafuna ukuthi sisheshe
  37,177,Ngakho-ke uma (isijeziso) sesehlela egcekeni labo ngakho-ke kuyokuba kubi ukusa kulabo abaxwayiswayo
  37,178,Ngakho-ke suka kubona kuze kube yisikhashana
  37,179,"Futhi bheka, ngakho-ke nabo bayobona"
  37,180,"Mayidunyiswe iNkosi yakho, iNkosi yamandla ngaphezulu kwalokho abakuchazayo"
  37,181,Futhi ukuthula makube phezulu kwezithunywa
  37,182,Futhi udumo lungolukaMvelinqangi iNkosi yemihlaba